Global Corneal Implants Market Insights
Corneal Implants Market size was valued at USD 1.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.5 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 9.8% from 2024 to 2030.

Corneal Implants Market Overview
The global corneal implants market is projected to reach a market value of approximately USD 1.7 billion by 2030, growing at a steady compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 6.5% from 2025 to 2030. This growth is driven by the increasing prevalence of eye disorders such as keratoconus, age-related macular degeneration, and diabetic retinopathy, alongside the rising demand for advanced vision correction solutions. Additionally, the growing adoption of minimally invasive surgeries and technological advancements in corneal implant materials are contributing to the market's expansion. With a shift towards patient-centric healthcare systems and improved healthcare infrastructure, the demand for corneal implants is expected to continue rising globally.

